# PR Summary Format

When asked to summarize a PR, use this structure:
### Added
- item 1
- item 2
- item ...

### Modified
- ...

### Removed
- ...

Keep each item concise and action-oriented. If a section has no items, don't include the header for it.

Always generate the summary in markdown and wrap it in a markdown code block (```markdown ... ```) so the user can copy raw markdown into GitHub.